        ≤ #(hypercubeEdgeFinset _) + 2 * d := by
          sorry
      _ ≤ d * #_ + 2 * d := by omega_nat; exact ih h𝓕'
      _ = d * (#_ + 1) + d := by ring
      _ ≤ d * #(insert _ _) := by simp [card_insert_of_not_mem hA]; omega
```
